Contents: {LB: {10 g/L Peptone, 5 g/L Yeast Extract, 5 g/L NaCl}, M9: {M9 salts (5X) 20 mL/100 mL, glucose (20%) 2 mL/100mL, MgSO4 (1 Molar) 200 uL/100 mL, H2O 78 mL/100 mL }}
